{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0e8997d5b5","title":"陕甘支队的行动部署叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f602ac0fd","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":19,"articleId":"0e8997d5b5"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b8b558d419","type":"paragraph","text":"陕甘支队的行动部署叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"5279cb2cf0","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月19日）彭司令员：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"a2018709ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一纵队本日到吴起镇及其前后十五里宿营，明（二十）日以准备作战姿势在此休息一天，对来敌筑工事警戒并派队向来路游击。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"36dcb6a970","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）二、三纵队明日宜靠近吴起镇，在其以南二十里左右地区宿营。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"5f306e6039","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）吴起镇已是苏区边境，此地以东即有红色政权，保安城闻有红色部队，但吴起镇、金汤镇“之间之金佛坪有地主武装百余守堡，拟派队消灭之","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"11c3253109","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）明日请彭来吴起镇商行动方针，二、三纵队交叶邓指挥","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"b2e87c9acb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"3bbad473eb","type":"paragraph","text":"十九日十九时[1]这是毛泽东给红军陕甘支队司令员彭德怀的电报。[2]吴起镇，今名吴旗镇，为陕西省吴旗县县治。[31保安城，原保安县城，今为陕西省志丹县县治。14]金汤镇，位于今陕西省志丹县西部。5叶邓，指叶剑英、邓发，当时分别任红军陕甘支队第三纵队司令员1935年，陕甘支队和红十五军团部分领导人在会师后的合影。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"},{"id":"149939969d","type":"paragraph","text":"1935年10月27日，蒋介石飞抵西安，亲自部署“督”红军。图为蒋介石在西安城南王曲军官训练团讲话。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5"}],"page":{"id":"4f1f6c25ad","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0e8997d5b5","start":248,"end":249}}}},"__N_SSG":true}